      <section eId="sec_245_03">
        <num>245.03</num>
        <heading>Public lewdness in the first degree</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_245_03__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_245_03__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of section 245.00 of this article, he or she\nintentionally exposes the private or intimate parts of his or her body\nin a lewd manner for the purpose of alarming or seriously annoying such\nperson, and he or she is thereby observed by such person in such place;\nor\n  2. he or she commits the crime of public lewdness, as defined in\nsection 245.00 of this article, and within the preceding year has been\nconvicted of an offense defined in such section 245.00 or this section.\n  Public lewdness in the first degree is a class A misdemeanor.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
